                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d797">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Count <persName type="from">Cassini</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Adee</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Russian Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bar Harbor, Me.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I receive this very moment your telegram of the 14th. It is materially impossible
                    to receive an answer from St. Petersburg today. I beg the President to allow a
                    delay of forty-eight hours to permit me to receive instructions from my
                    Government.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cassini.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
